  "instructions": [
    "Heat the render-fat in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the grated ginger and minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the corn kernels and cook for 2-3 minutes, or until they start to brown.",
    "Add the chopped scallions and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the cooked masarepa to the skillet or wok, breaking it up with a spatula as you go.",
    "Stir in the soy sauce and sesame oil, and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the creamy Chinese corn fried rice hot, garnished with additional scallions if desired."
